    "statement": "- 🚀 **256K Context Window**: Supports long-horizon reasoning and deep multi-step analysis\n- 🔧 **600 Tool Calls**: Handles up to 600 tool calls per task — a substantial improvement over previous open-source research agents\n- 📦 **Multiple Scales**: Released in 8B, 30B, and 72B parameter scales, accompanied by a comprehensive suite of tools and workflows to flexibly support diverse research settings and compute budgets",
